<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I just read this for the first time, and hadn&apos;t previously read any Marx or Engels or known anything about the historical events Lenin discusses. I th<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I just read this for the first time, and hadn't previously read any Marx or Engels or known anything about the historical events Lenin discusses. I thought the edition I read, published by Haymarket books, with an introduction and annotations by Todd Chretien, was really good and accessible. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
