<div id="review_1886752836" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1886752836" />
    <a title="Abeer Abdullah" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16996132-abeer-abdullah"><img alt="Abeer Abdullah" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1640235058p2/16996132.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1886752836?book_show_action=true">Feb 03, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Abeer Abdullah" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Abeer Abdullah" href="/user/show/16996132-abeer-abdullah">Abeer Abdullah</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16996132-abeer-abdullah?shelf=important">important</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16996132-abeer-abdullah?shelf=theleftleftleft">theleftleftleft</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16996132-abeer-abdullah?shelf=marxism">marxism</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1886752836" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6086533133580816193">Extremely thorough and well written, deals with the question of the state after the revolution, makes distinctions between communists, social democrats and anarchists. Argues that anarchists and communists have the common goal of the abolition of the state, it is simply the methods that they disagree on. Wonderful read, I learned a lot!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


